    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. i guess i'm just nervous about the money sitting there. what actually happens to that money if the inspection comes back and shows something really bad, like foundation issues? do they just give it back to me or is it stuck in there somewhere?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
